Description:
STANDARD FEATURES

The main structure has high rigidity. Y, Z axis adopt rectangular guide way, X axis adopt swallow tail guide way.
The table surface and the guide ways are hardened.
Automatic lubrication mechanism.
X, Y, Z axis adopt ball screw, low speed feed without crawl and high precision.
Magazine: Armless type, BT40/ 16pcs
Machine_Operation: Side face machining, Step shoulder machining, Straight slot machining
